			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Take two large spider silks and combine them in a sewing kit and you get silk material from which you can then fashion items or sell. Even if you don't want to learn sewing, if you hunt a lot of large spiders, buy a small sewing kit and use it to combine the spider silks. You'll have something much more valuable to sell.
			</font>
	
