Spiders are only level 2-4, not 4-7 (they allredy con GREEN to me at 6 and run away after first hit)<BR>
<BR>
2 gold per silk on level 2-4 creature??? whoah!!!<BR>
<BR>
And yes you can use talorinf kit and combine 2 silks into  1 silk swatche, which sell for 4 gold aprox. and they are stackable.<BR>
<BR>
Now silk swatches are used to make SILK Armor which weight almost nothing - great fro Monks and Casters<BR>
<BR>
Now notice: All talors who spend hours of time of tonns on money increasing taloring scills!!!<BR>
<BR>
Silks combine toghers ALWAYS without falures and will bring your taloring scill to 15 for free!!!<BR>
<BR>
plus you will have nice stacj of silk swathes ready to make armor.<BR>
<BR>
keep in mind that to make silk armor inteslf you must have scill of  30+<BR>
